data.description: Fabulous remodeled 5 bed/3 bath home in wonderful Mountain Ridge community on quiet cul-de-sac. Beautiful two-tone interior & exterior paint less than 4 years old. Great layout w/gorgeous wood-look tile floors. Carpets in bdrms and upstairs. Two living spaces for entertainment! Huge family rm has nice fireplace. Airy kitchen w/stainless appliances, pantry & granite countertops. Big master w/separate garden tub/shower, water closet and big walk-in closet. Plus 4 addtnl bdrms (2 up/2 dwn). 3 bathrooms! Huge backyard space with mountain views, easy maintenance landscaping, covered patio, block walls w/two double gates for RV or toys, side garage door, two-car garage, big front yard, and more! Move in ready! Short distance to Huachuca Mountain Elementary, shopping, and Ft. Huachuca.
